data.description: Exquisite Luxury Townhome in the Heart of Atlanta  Discover unparalleled luxury in Atlanta's most exclusive gated enclave. With only 9 residences, this magnificent 4-floor townhome offers an intimate living experience amidst the vibrancy of Atlanta's most sought-after area. An embodiment of sophistication, each home boasts a private elevator, providing effortless access to all levels of opulent living space.  A New Dimension of Luxury Living  Spanning over 3,527 sq ft, this townhome features 4 sumptuous bedrooms and 4.5 lavish bathrooms, each meticulously designed to offer an unparalleled living experience. The rooftop terrace, a hallmark of luxury, presents a premium wet bar and breathtaking views, setting the stage for unforgettable evenings under the stars.  Bespoke Interiors & Gourmet Kitchen  The residence's interiors are a testament to bespoke elegance, with floor-to-ceiling windows illuminating the space with natural light. The custom kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting glass-accented cabinetry, a striking marble waterfall island, and an exquisite Wolf appliance package. The master suite, a serene retreat, features an oversized closet, while the en-suite bathroom offers a spa-like experience with a separate shower and tub.  Unrivaled Location  Positioned adjacent to Atlanta's premier shopping and dining destinations, including Nobu, the Lenox MARTA station, and Phipps Place, this townhome offers convenience and luxury at your doorstep. Embrace the epitome of Atlanta living in a community that redefines upscale urban living.  Exclusive Financing Offer  Enhance your buying power with a 2-1 Rate Buydown, significantly reducing your interest rate by 2% for the first year and 1% for the second year. While buyers are not obligated to use Jeff Zulauf of Cross Country Mortgage to have their offer accepted, taking advantage of this offer requires partnering with Jeff Zulauf. The Z Team offers rapid approvals within as little as 3 days and the ability to close in just 10 days, subject to restrictions. Jeff Zulauf NMLS 18566.  Your Exclusive Invitation  This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle reserved for the discerning few. Seize the opportunity to reside in Atlanta's most coveted gated community.
